com.hamweather.aeris.model

Class AerisBatchResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hamweather.aeris.model.AerisBatchResponse

  • public class AerisBatchResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    The basic response from the Aeris API. Generally all responses from Aeris will have a success boolean, than error string or an object(s) attached to it. This is the response returned from a batch request.
    Author:
    Ben Collins
